<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Booking Notification - Car Rental</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #e0e0e0;
            max-width: 650px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2c2c2c 0%, #3a3a3a 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        .container {
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, #404040, #2a2a2a);
            padding: 35px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 
                0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.4),
                inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            border: 1px solid #555;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .container::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 3px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ff6b35, #f7931e, #ffd23f, #06d6a0, #118ab2, #073b4c);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 35px;
            padding: 25px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4a4a4a, #2d2d2d);
            border-radius: 15px;
            border: 1px solid #666;
            position: relative;
        }
        .header::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -10px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 60px;
            height: 4px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ff6b35, #06d6a0);
            border-radius: 2px;
        }
        .header h1 {
            color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #ff6b35, #06d6a0);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }
        .header p {
            color: #b0b0b0;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .content {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .content p {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .booking-details {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3a3a3a, #2d2d2d);
            border: 2px solid #555;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-radius: 15px;
            position: relative;
            box-shadow: inset 0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }
        .booking-details::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -2px;
            left: -2px;
            right: -2px;
            bottom: -2px;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #ff6b35, #06d6a0, #118ab2, #f7931e);
            border-radius: 15px;
            z-index: -1;
            opacity: 0.3;
        }
        .booking-details h3 {
            color: #ffffff;
            margin-top: 0;
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .customer-info {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2d4a4a, #1e3333);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border: 1px solid #4a6666;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }
        .customer-info strong {
            color: #06d6a0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 35px;
            padding: 25px 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2a2a2a, #1a1a1a);
            border-radius: 12px;
            border-top: 3px solid #555;
            color: #999;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .highlight {
            color: #06d6a0;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(6, 214, 160, 0.3);
        }
        .label {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #ff6b35;
            display: inline-block;
            min-width: 120px;
        }
        .action-list {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3d2a2a, #2a1a1a);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            border-left: 4px solid #ff6b35;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .action-list ul {
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        .action-list li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            color: #e0e0e0;
        }
        .booking-id-tag {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #ff6b35, #f7931e);
            color: #000;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 12px;
            margin-left: 10px;
        }
        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #06d6a0, #04a777);
            color: #000;
            padding: 6px 14px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 14px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        .price-highlight {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #ffd23f;
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255, 210, 63, 0.4);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>üöó New Booking Alert</h1>
            <p>A premium vehicle booking awaits your attention</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>Greetings <span class="highlight">{{adminName}}</span>,</p>
            <p>A sophisticated new booking has been submitted through our premium Car Rental platform. Immediate review and processing is recommended for optimal customer experience.</p>
            
            <div class="booking-details">
                <h3>üìã Booking Overview</h3>
                <p><span class="label">Booking Reference:</span> {{booking.id}} <span class="booking-id-tag">ID-{{booking.id}}</span></p>
                <p><span class="label">Rental Period:</span> {{booking.startDate}} ‚Üí {{booking.endDate}}</p>
                <p><span class="label">Investment Total:</span> <span class="price-highlight">${{booking.totalPrice}}</span></p>
                <p><span class="label">Current Status:</span> <span class="status-badge">{{booking.status}}</span></p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="customer-info">
                <strong>üë§ Client Profile:</strong><br><br>
                <strong>Full Name:</strong> {{customer.name}}<br>
                <strong>Contact Email:</strong> {{customer.email}}<br>
                {{#if customer.phone}}
                <strong>Phone Number:</strong> {{customer.phone}}<br>
                {{/if}}
            </div>
            
            <div class="action-list">
                <p><strong>‚ö° Priority Actions Required:</strong></p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Conduct comprehensive booking review and validation</li>
                    <li>Process approval or rejection via administrative dashboard</li>
                    <li>Initiate customer communication for additional requirements</li>
                    <li>Update booking status and notify relevant departments</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>üèÜ Premium Car Rental Service - Administrative Portal</strong></p>
            <p>This is an automated high-priority notification from our booking management system.</p>
            <p style="font-size: 11px; color: #777; margin-top: 15px;">
                Reference: {{booking.id}} | Timestamp: {{submittedAt}} | System: AutoNotify v2.0
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>